" class="nav-list-link">1. Install Anki-Connect</a> </li><li class="nav-list-item "> <a href="/install-awesome-tts.html" class="nav-list-link">2. Install AwesomeTTS</a> </li><li class="nav-list-item "> <a href="/configure-ankilingoflash.html" class="nav-list-link">3. Configure AnkiLingoFlash</a> </li><li class="nav-list-item "> <a href="/generate-your-first-flashcard.html" class="nav-list-link">4. Generate Your First Flashcard</a> </li><li class="nav-list-item "> <a href="/configure-tts-tool.html" class="nav-list-link">5. Configure Text-to-Speech Tool</a> </li></ul></li></ul></li><li class="nav-list-item"><a href="/blog.html" class="nav-list-link">Blog</a></li><li class="nav-list-item"><a href="/about.html" class="nav-list-link">About</a></li></ul> <ul class="nav-list"></ul> </nav> <p></p> </div> <div class="main" id="top"> <div id="main-header" class="main-header"> <div></div> <nav aria-label="Auxiliary" class="aux-nav"> <ul class="aux-nav-list"> </ul> </nav> </div> <div id="main-content-wrap" class="main-content-wrap"> <div id="main-content" class="main-content"> <main> <h{"0": { "doc": "About", "title": "About AnkiLingoFlash", "content": "AnkiLingoFlash is an web browser extension aiming to make language learning more accessible, efficient, and enjoyable for everyone. It has been designed to help you reach your language learning goals faster than ever before. Get Started Now . ", "url": "/about.html#about-ankilingoflash", "relUrl": "/about.html#about-ankilingoflash" },"1": { "doc": "About", "title": "About", "content": " ", "url": "/about.html", "relUrl": "/about.html" },"2": { "doc": "Blog", "title": "AnkiLingoFlash Blog", "content": "Here youâ€™ll find articles, tips, and insights to enhance your language learning journey. ", "url": "/blog.html#ankilingoflash-blog", "relUrl": "/blog.html#ankilingoflash-blog" },"3": { "doc": "Blog", "title": "ðŸš€ Master a New Language in Months, Not Years: Use AnkiLingoFlash for Quickly Building a Strong Vocabulary Foundation", "content": "July 16, 2024 . ", "url": "/blog.html", "relUrl": "/blog.html" },"4": { "doc": "Blog", "title": "Blog", "content": " ", "url": "/blog.html", "relUrl": "/blog.html" },"5": { "doc": "3. Configure AnkiLingoFlash", "title": "Configuring AnkiLingoFlash", "content": "After installing Anki-Connect and AwesomeTTS, itâ€™s important to configure AnkiLingoFlash to suit your learning needs. Hereâ€™s how to do it: . | Click on the AnkiLingoFlash icon in your browser toolbar to open the extension popup. | In the popup, youâ€™ll see two options: . | Free trial: Start with a limited number of free flashcards. | Own credits: Use your own OpenAI API credits for unlimited flashcards. | . | If you choose the free trial: . | Click on the Sign in with Google button. | Follow the prompts to authenticate with your Google account. | Once logged in, youâ€™ll see a welcome message and the number of free flashcards remaining. | . | If you choose to use your own credits or have exhausted your free trial: . | Youâ€™ll need to use your own OpenAI API key, which is very cost-effective (a dollar can generate thousands of flashcards). | Follow these steps to create and use an OpenAI API key: . a. Create an OpenAI Account: Go to the ChatGPT website and sign up for an account. b. Generate an API Key: . | Navigate to the API keys section. | Click on â€œCreate new secret keyâ€. | Choose a name for your key, such as â€œAnkiLingoFlashâ€. | Click on â€œCreate secret keyâ€. | Note down the generated key. | . c. Add Funds to Your Account: . | In the OpenAI dashboard, go to the â€œSettingsâ€ menu. | Navigate to the â€œBillingâ€ section. | Add a minimum of $5 USD (or equivalent) to your account. | . d. Use the API Key in AnkiLingoFlash: . | Copy your API key and paste it into the settings of the AnkiLingoFlash extension. | . | . | Select the language for definitions and mnemonics: . | Choose from available options: English, French, Spanish, Portuguese (Portugal), German, Italian, or Danish. | . | . Now that youâ€™ve configured AnkiLingoFlash, itâ€™s time to put it to use! Letâ€™s move on to Generating Your First Flashcard. ", "url": "/configure-ankilingoflash.html#configuring-ankilingoflash", "relUrl": "/configure-ankilingoflash.html#configuring-ankilingoflash" },"6": { "doc": "3. Configure AnkiLingoFlash", "title": "3. Configure AnkiLingoFlash", "content": " ", "url": "/configure-ankilingoflash.html", "relUrl": "/configure-ankilingoflash.html" },"7": { "doc": "5. Configure Text-to-Speech Tool", "title": "Configuring the Text-to-Speech Tool", "content": "To add pronunciation guides to your flashcards, you need to configure the text-to-speech tool for your target language. Follow these steps: . | Generate your first flashcard as described in the previous step. | In Anki, go to Tools &gt; Manage Note Types. | You should see the flashcard type corresponding to the language of the word or phrase you selected. For example, if you selected an English term, look for AnkiLingoFlash_English [1 note]. | Select the appropriate card type and click on Cardsâ€¦. | In the card editor: . | Check the Back Template. | Click on OK to dismiss any message that appears. | Click on Add TTS. | . | Configure the text-to-speech service: . | Select the service you want to use. For example, for English, you can choose the free local service Youdao Dictionary. | Choose the appropriate voice (e.g., English, American [default] for English). | Click on Save, then on OK. | . | Set up the TTS fields: . | For the Field option, select Selection. | For the Language field, select the desired language for text-to-speech. | . | Finalize the setup: . | Click on Insert into Back Template. | Close the message that appears by clicking on OK. | In the Back Template, find the line [Text-to-speech not yet configured] and replace it with the line that was just added (it should contain the TTS tag). | Click on Save. | . | . Important: You will need to repeat this process for each language you wish to learn. Congratulations! You have now completely finished setting up AnkiLingoFlash. You can now review the first word or phrase you added to Anki, or continue to add other flashcards. ", "url": "/configure-tts-tool.html#configuring-the-text-to-speech-tool", "relUrl": "/configure-tts-tool.html#configuring-the-text-to-speech-tool" },"8": { "doc": "5. Configure Text-to-Speech Tool", "title": "5. Configure Text-to-Speech Tool", "content": " ", "url": "/configure-tts-tool.html", "relUrl": "/configure-tts-tool.html" },"9": { "doc": "4. Generate Your First Flashcard", "title": "Generating Your First Flashcard", "content": "Now that youâ€™ve installed and configured AnkiLingoFlash, itâ€™s time to generate and add your first flashcard to Anki. Follow these steps: . | Select a word or phrase on a recently loaded web page. | Right-click on the selected term. This will open the context menu. | Click on Generate a flashcard in the context menu. This action will trigger AnkiLingoFlash to create a new flashcard. | Follow the on-screen instructions to create and add the flashcard to an Anki deck. | . Great job on creating your first flashcard! The final step is to Configure the Text-to-Speech Tool to add pronunciation guides to your flashcards. ", "url": "/generate-your-first-flashcard.html#generating-your-first-flashcard", "relUrl": "/generate-your-first-flashcard.html#generating-your-first-flashcard" },"10": { "doc": "4. Generate Your First Flashcard", "title": "4. Generate Your First Flashcard", "content": " ", "url": "/generate-your-first-flashcard.html", "relUrl": "/generate-your-first-flashcard.html" },"11": { "doc": "Getting Started", "title": "Getting Started with AnkiLingoFlash", "content": "Welcome to AnkiLingoFlash! This guide will help you set up and start using our AI-powered language learning tool. ", "url": "/getting-started.html#getting-started-with-ankilingoflash", "relUrl": "/getting-started.html#getting-started-with-ankilingoflash" },"12": { "doc": "Getting Started", "title": "Quick Start Guide", "content": "Follow these steps to begin your journey with AnkiLingoFlash: . | Installation Learn how to install the AnkiLingoFlash browser extension on your preferred browser. | Quick Tutorial Get a quick overview of how to use AnkiLingoFlash and create your first flashcards. | . ", "url": "/getting-started.html#quick-start-guide", "relUrl": "/getting-started.html#quick-start-guide" },"13": { "doc": "Getting Started", "title": "Whatâ€™s Next?", "content": "After completing the quick start guide, youâ€™ll be ready to: . | Generate AI-powered flashcards as you browse the web | Customize your learning experience | Start building your vocabulary efficiently | . Choose a section above to begin your AnkiLingoFlash journey! . Install Now Start Tutorial . Happy learning with AnkiLingoFlash! . ", "url": "/getting-started.html#whats-next", "relUrl": "/getting-started.html#whats-next" },"14": { "doc": "Getting Started", "title": "Getting Started", "content": " ", "url": "/getting-started.html", "relUrl": "/getting-started.html" },"15": { "doc": "Home", "title": "Transform Your Web Browsing into Language Learning", "content": "Supercharge your Anki experience with the AnkiLingoFlash browser extension. ", "url": "/#transform-your-web-browsing-into-language-learning", "relUrl": "/#transform-your-web-browsing-into-language-learning" },"16": { "doc": "Home", "title": "Experience the power of AnkiLingoFlash:", "content": ". | Install our browser extension with a single click | Browse your favorite websites as usual | Right-click on any words or phrases you want to learn | Instantly receive AI-generated flashcards without leaving your browser! | . Install Now . ", "url": "/#experience-the-power-of-ankilingoflash", "relUrl": "/#experience-the-power-of-ankilingoflash" },"17": { "doc": "Home", "title": "Unique Features", "content": ". | AI-Powered Flashcards: Create comprehensive flashcards with definitions, mnemonics, and pronunciation guides. | Seamless Anki Integration: Generate and add cards to Anki directly from your browser, without typing and disrupting your daily routine. | Personalized Learning: Create personalized flashcard sets tailored to your interests, no more downloading uncertain quality decks. | . Elevate your language skills with AnkiLingoFlash â€“ where every webpage becomes a learning opportunity! . ", "url": "/#unique-features", "relUrl": "/#unique-features" },"18": { "doc": "Home", "title": "Home", "content": " ", "url": "/", "relUrl": "/" },"19": { "doc": "1. Install Anki-Connect", "title": "Installing Anki-Connect", "content": "Anki-Connect is crucial for AnkiLingoFlash to communicate with your Anki application. Hereâ€™s how to install it: . | Open Anki and go to Tools &gt; Add-ons &gt; Get Add-onsâ€¦ | Enter the code 2055492159 and click OK. | A message prompting you to restart Anki should appear; close it by clicking on OK. | Go to Tools &gt; Add-ons | Double-click on AnkiConnect in the add-ons list. | Replace the entire configuration with the following: | . { \"apiKey\": null, \"apiLogPath\": null, \"ignoreOriginList\": [], \"webBindAddress\": \"127.0.0.1\", \"webBindPort\": 8765, \"webCorsOriginList\": [ \"chrome-extension://hicnjnfcmjfnomdfmekhigghmlkmachb\", \"http://localhost/*\", \"https://*/*\" ] } . Great job! Now that youâ€™ve installed Anki-Connect, letâ€™s move on to the next step: Installing AwesomeTTS. ", "url": "/install-anki-connect.html#installing-anki-connect", "relUrl": "/install-anki-connect.html#installing-anki-connect" },"20": { "doc": "1. Install Anki-Connect", "title": "1. Install Anki-Connect", "content": " ", "url": "/install-anki-connect.html", "relUrl": "/install-anki-connect.html" },"21": { "doc": "2. Install AwesomeTTS", "title": "Installing AwesomeTTS", "content": "AwesomeTTS is a powerful text-to-speech tool for Anki. Hereâ€™s how to install it: . | In Anki, go to Tools &gt; Add-ons &gt; Get Add-onsâ€¦ | Enter the code 1436550454 and click OK | Restart Anki when prompted | . Excellent! With AwesomeTTS installed, youâ€™re ready for the next step: Configuring AnkiLingoFlash. ", "url": "/install-awesome-tts.html#installing-awesometts", "relUrl": "/install-awesome-tts.html#installing-awesometts" },"22": { "doc": "2. Install AwesomeTTS", "title": "2. Install AwesomeTTS", "content": " ", "url": "/install-awesome-tts.html", "relUrl": "/install-awesome-tts.html" },"23": { "doc": "Installation", "title": "Installing AnkiLingoFlash", "content": "Follow these simple steps to install the AnkiLingoFlash browser extension: . | Visit the Chrome Web Store | Click on the â€œAdd to Chromeâ€ button | Follow the prompts to add the extension to your browser | Once installed, youâ€™ll see the AnkiLingoFlash icon in your browser toolbar | . Note: AnkiLingoFlash is currently available for Google Chrome. Support for other major browsers, including Microsoft Edge and Firefox, will be rolled out in the coming weeks. Stay tuned for updates! . Congratulations! Youâ€™re now ready to start using AnkiLingoFlash. Next, learn how to configure AnkiLingoFlash for the best experience. ", "url": "/installation.html#installing-ankilingoflash", "relUrl": "/installation.html#installing-ankilingoflash" },"24": { "doc": "Installation", "title": "Installation", "content": " ", "url": "/installation.html", "relUrl": "/installation.html" },"25": { "doc": "Quick Tutorial for Setting Up AnkiLingoFlash", "title": "Quick Tutorial for Setting Up AnkiLingoFlash", "content": "Get up and running with AnkiLingoFlash in no time! This quick tutorial will guide you through the basic setup and usage of our AI-powered language learning tool. Follow these steps to start supercharging your language learning today! . ", "url": "/quick-tutorial.html", "relUrl": "/quick-tutorial.html" } } </main> <hr> <footer> <p class="text-small text-grey-dk-100 mb-0">Â© 2024 AnkiLingoFlash. All rights reserved.</p> </footer> </div> </div> </div> </body> </html>
